# ============================================================
# Sudo_Hatter_Command HOME BASE — .gitignore
# The home base tracks ONLY its own infra (.agents, _artifacts, docs,
# _experiment, _system, lobby .claude/.opencode, root map files,
# youtube_transcripts). Every sub-project keeps its OWN git repo and is
# NEVER tracked here.
# ============================================================

# All projects live under Projects/ and are independent repos.
# (Ignore rules removed to allow VS Code Git repository auto-discovery)

# All projects live under Projects/ and are independent repos. The old root-level pre-migration entries
# (aviationChat-AGY, fresh-workspace-bmad, jetChat-AGY, B&L WorldWide, NEXGen Films, ingestion-Pipeline-*, openCode)
# have been retired now that those workspaces are under Projects/.

# GitNexus code-graph index (disposable Tier-2 accelerator — never committed).
**/.gitnexus/

# Build / runtime junk anywhere
**/node_modules/
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/__pycache__/
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
*.pyc

# Secrets / local
**/.env
**/auth_keys/
.claude/settings.local.json
